1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Accounts payable runs on evidence, but money movement demands
accountability. Archon Autopilot investigates invoices, then
stops for human authorization. This is our Qwen Cloud Track Four
agent.

2
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Public intake is an isolated, redacted preview. Authenticated
intake creates durable pending work. Qwen may gather evidence
and propose an action; only the reviewer interface can decide or
execute.

3
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:52,000
On Alibaba Cloud, a synthetic invoice enters the reviewer flow.
Qwen Vision extracts it. Qwen Plus recalls vendor history,
validates the numbers, and selects only relevant duplicate,
variance, or context checks. The visible trace ends at one
durable pending proposal. Nothing has executed.

4
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:11,000
The reviewer sees the exact proposal, evidence, and arguments,
then approves, amends, or rejects. The decided view preserves
the before-and-after diff. Executed arguments must equal
authorized arguments. Atomic claiming blocks replay, and
uncertain delivery is never blindly retried.

5
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:34,000
The gate also creates correction evidence. After a reviewer
corrects a material overbill to the verified baseline, a
matching re-bill is escalated on the next bounded run. The
corrected control remains a payment proposal. This changes
future behavior without changing model weights.

6
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:53,000
We keep every claim bounded. Twenty-two developer-labelled
offline regressions pass, alongside a fixed twelve-case
synthetic workflow model and sixteen hash-locked vision
fixtures. These are reproducibility artifacts, not live-model
accuracy, labor savings, or return on investment. No candidate
model was promoted.

7
00:01:53,000 --> 00:02:14,000
A hostile invoice can influence a proposal, so recognized
patterns are surfaced. The stronger invariant is structural:
neither the model nor the four-tool M C P catalog can approve,
amend, reject, recover, or pay. Every proposal remains behind
the authenticated human gate.

8
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:34,000
Deployment proof separates the recorded deployment hash, the
clean capture-source commit, and the later submitted head.
Public health, authenticated deep readiness, and real decision
and vision canaries exercise Qwen Plus and Qwen V L Max on
Alibaba Cloud. The evidence remains hash-bound.

9
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:48,000
Archon Autopilot is live and open source under the M I T
license. It is built for Track Four. Judgment is bounded; money
movement stays deterministic and human-controlled.
